TABLE: PRODUKTER
VERSION: 6
FIELDS: 7
RECORDS: 14

#    NAME                 TYPE             LEN  DEC  FLAGS
------------------------------------------------------------
1    PRODUKT_ID           Integer            4    0  INDEXED
2    NAVN                 Text              60    0  REQUIRED
3    VARENUMMER           Text              20    0  -
4    ENHETSPRIS           Float              8    2  -
5    KOSTPRIS             Float              8    2  -
6    MVA_TYPE             Text              15    0  -
7    INNTEKTSKONTO        Text              10    0  -

RECORD_SIZE:   126 bytes  (1 flag + 125 data)
HEADER_SIZE:   578 bytes

FIELD NOTES:
  PRODUKT_ID    - Auto-increment integer, indexed
  NAVN          - Product name, required, latin-1 encoded
  VARENUMMER    - Optional product code
  ENHETSPRIS    - Unit price, 8-byte IEEE 754 double, 2 decimals
  KOSTPRIS      - Cost price, same encoding (0.0 = not set)
  MVA_TYPE      - 'Hoy' or 'Fritatt'  (ø stored as latin-1 0xF8)
  INNTEKTSKONTO - Norwegian chart-of-accounts code (3000/3020/3100)

ENCODING:
  Text fields   : fixed-width, null-padded (0x00), latin-1
  Float fields  : 8-byte little-endian IEEE 754 double
  Integer fields: 4-byte little-endian signed int32
  Record flag   : 0x20=active, 0x2A=deleted
  File ends with EOF marker 0x1A